{"id":689,"parent_id":680,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":689,"title":"Ecclesiastes 9","subtitle":"","short_title":"Eccl.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 9"],[".studySummary",["i","God’s providence rules over all—All men are subject to time and chance—Wisdom is better than strength—One sinner destroys much good."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.1","order":"02.22.009.44584"},["b","1"],"For all this I considered in my heart even to declare all this, that the righteous, and the wise, and their works,",["i","are"],"in the hand of God: no man knoweth either love or hatred",["i","by"],"all",["i","that is"],"before them."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.2","order":"02.22.009.44585"},["b","2"],"All",["i","things come"],"alike to all:",["i","there is"],"one",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"event"],"to the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"righteous"],", and to the wicked; to the good and to the clean, and to the unclean; to him that sacrificeth, and to him that sacrificeth not: as",["i","is"],"the good, so",["i","is"],"the sinner;",["i","and"],"he that",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"sweareth"],", as",["i","he"],"that",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_2d"},"feareth an oath"],"."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.3","order":"02.22.009.44586"},["b","3"],"This",["i","is"],"an evil among all",["i","things"],"that are done under the sun, that",["i","there is"],"one event unto all: yea, also the heart of the sons of men is full of evil, and madness",["i","is"],"in their heart while they live, and after that",["i","they go"],"to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"dead"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.4","order":"02.22.009.44587"},["b","4"],"¶For to him that is joined to all the living there is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"hope"],": for a living dog is better than a dead lion."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.5","order":"02.22.009.44588"},["b","5"],"For the living know that they shall die: but the dead know not any thing, neither have they any more a reward; for the memory of them is forgotten."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.6","order":"02.22.009.44589"},["b","6"],"Also their love, and their hatred, and their envy, is now perished; neither have they any more a portion for ever in any",["i","thing"],"that is done under the sun."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.7","order":"02.22.009.44590"},["b","7"],"¶Go thy way, eat thy bread with joy, and drink thy wine with a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"merry"],"heart; for God now accepteth thy works."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.8","order":"02.22.009.44591"},["b","8"],"Let thy garments be always",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"white"],"; and let thy head lack no ointment."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.9","order":"02.22.009.44592"},["b","9"],"Live",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"joyfully"],"with the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"wife"],"whom thou",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"lovest"],"all the days of the life of thy",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_9d"},"vanity"],", which he hath given thee under the sun, all the days of thy vanity: for that",["i","is"],"thy",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_9e"},"portion"],"in",["i","this"],"life, and in thy labour which thou takest under the sun."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.10","order":"02.22.009.44593"},["b","10"],"Whatsoever thy hand findeth to do, do",["i","it"],"with thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"might"],"; for",["i","there is"],"no work, nor device, nor",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"knowledge"],", nor wisdom, in the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"grave"],", whither thou goest."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.11","order":"02.22.009.44594"},["b","11"],"¶I returned, and saw under the sun, that the race",["i","is"],"not to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"swift"],", nor the battle to the strong, neither yet bread to the wise, nor yet riches to men of understanding, nor yet favour to men of skill; but time and chance happeneth to them all."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.12","order":"02.22.009.44595"},["b","12"],"For man also knoweth not his time: as the fishes that are taken in an evil net, and as the birds that are caught in the snare; so",["i","are"],"the sons of men",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"snared"],"in an evil time, when it falleth suddenly upon them."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.13","order":"02.22.009.44596"},["b","13"],"¶This wisdom have I seen also under the sun, and it",["i","seemed"],"great unto me:"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.14","order":"02.22.009.44597"},["b","14"],["i","There was"],"a little city, and few men within it; and there came a great king against it, and besieged it, and built great bulwarks against it:"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.15","order":"02.22.009.44598"},["b","15"],"Now there was found in it a poor wise man, and he by his wisdom delivered the city; yet no man remembered that same poor man."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.16","order":"02.22.009.44599"},["b","16"],"Then said I,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"Wisdom"],["i","is"],"better than strength: nevertheless the poor man’s",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"wisdom"],["i","is"],"despised, and his words are not heard."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.17","order":"02.22.009.44600"},["b","17"],"The words of wise",["i","men are"],"heard in quiet more than the cry of him that ruleth among fools."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.18","order":"02.22.009.44601"},["b","18"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"Wisdom"],["i","is"],"better than weapons of war: but one",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"sinner"],"destroyeth much good."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.2a","order":"02.22.009.44602"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.14"},"Eccl. 2:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.2b","order":"02.22.009.44604"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/12.8"},"Alma 12:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.2c","order":"02.22.009.44606"},["b","2c"],["span.small","IE"],"makes a covenant."],["div",{"id":"2d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.2d","order":"02.22.009.44608"},["b","2d"],["span.small","IE"],"avoids committing himself."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.3a","order":"02.22.009.44610"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/40.11.11-12"},"Alma 40:11 (11–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.4a","order":"02.22.009.44612"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hope"},"TG Hope"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.7a","order":"02.22.009.44614"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/cheerful"},"TG Cheerful"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.8a","order":"02.22.009.44616"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/5.21.21,24,27"},"Alma 5:21 (21, 24, 27)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.9a","order":"02.22.009.44618"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/joy"},"TG Joy"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.9b","order":"02.22.009.44620"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/marriage-husbands"},"TG Marriage, Husbands"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/marriage-wives"},"Marriage, Wives"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.9c","order":"02.22.009.44622"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/family-love-within"},"TG Family, Love within"],"."],["div",{"id":"9d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.9d","order":"02.22.009.44624"},["b","9d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/vanity"},"TG Vanity"],"."],["div",{"id":"9e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.9e","order":"02.22.009.44626"},["b","9e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/2.10"},"Eccl. 2:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.10a","order":"02.22.009.44628"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/industry"},"TG Industry"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.10b","order":"02.22.009.44630"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.13.13-14"},"2 Ne. 9:13 (13–14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/130.18"},"D&C 130:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.10c","order":"02.22.009.44632"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/34.33"},"Alma 34:33"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.11a","order":"02.22.009.44634"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/2.14.14-15"},"Amos 2:14 (14–15)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/4.27"},"Mosiah 4:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.12a","order":"02.22.009.44636"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/7.23.21-23"},"Prov. 7:23 (21–23)"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.16a","order":"02.22.009.44638"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/7.19"},"Eccl. 7:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.16b","order":"02.22.009.44640"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/6.2.2-3"},"Mark 6:2 (2–3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.18a","order":"02.22.009.44642"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/6.7"},"D&C 6:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/9.18b","order":"02.22.009.44644"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/7.11.1,11-12"},"Josh. 7:11 (1, 11–12)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/eccl/10.1"},"Eccl. 10:1"],"."]]}
